Plain sentence:
---------------
    After Nitta Yoshisada's army defeats the ruling Hojo clan of the Kamakura Shogunate and Emperor Godaigo re-establishes
    the imperial government at Kyoto, Nichimoku had decided to remonstrate with the new government, which might bring on a
    new opportunity to refute the other schools of Buddhism in front of the ruler of the nation.

